<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-05-22 11:43 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A4491 &Cx1f; var-z
u i &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-BRAZIL-OUTLOOK-REVIEW     05-22 1226
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-BRAZIL-OUTLOOK-REVIEW-2TAKES-NYT </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
INVESTORS PANICKED, BUT BRAZIL DIDN'T 
</HEADLINE>
  (The Week in Review) 
(NOTE TO INTERNATIONAL CLIENTS: For international clients' use by
