   ROCKDALE-MAIN _ CONYERS, Ga. _ The lawyer representing the teen
who allegegedly wounded six classmates at Heritage High School in
Conyers, Ga., on Thursday calls the boy a ``really charming young
man'' and adds that ``I am clueless why he did it. There's no
anger.'' Lawyer waives Monday hearing, will try to keep case in
